snippet.title: Amber Heard  vs Johnny Depp: Me Too Gone Too Far? Double Standards of Domestic Violence
snippet.description:
Alex and Khelil discuss the Amber Heard and Johnny Depp situation and the double standards that have been exasperated by the me too movement.

Why has Johnny Depp had to step down for allegations but not Amber Heard? Is there a double standard when it comes to never hitting women? Do men feel shame to say they have been abused?
